{"tid":1238982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 撐不住了？  郭文貴：林鄭月娥即將宣佈辭職","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:27:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":38,"dislike":494,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbce4ad8e0cf8408c8fca4e6bea6c732384bc5d","tid":1238982,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"香港人民發起「反送中」大遊行，要求香港政府撤回《逃犯條例》，前天有超過200萬的香港人走上街頭表達訴求，要求特首林鄭月娥下台。雖然林鄭月娥並未正面回應是否下台，不過中國反共富豪郭文貴今早爆料，林鄭月娥即將宣佈辭職。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴今早在個人社交網站「郭媒體」發文表示：「林鄭月娥辭職（的消息）即將公佈，這是不足夠的，我們不滿意。我們還需要更多的人辭職，以及查清反逃法的背後的真相，並且應該馬上釋放一切在香港監獄的政治犯，全面重選香港立法會。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，郭文貴還強調，香港特首必須實施真正的香港普選，且「香港律政司司長、香港保安局局長、香港警察局局長必須同時辭職」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2825676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2825676&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=81e31804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2825676&h=bbb5e74f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2825676</a>"},{"pid":"438d3f3bf0804d4a3290a3c218517877463c5244","tid":1238982,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53c1a356b457369a297808b09f64b5c687bc107","tid":1238982,"uid":22047,"like":593,"dislike":4,"score":589,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"唔好再quote呢條鳩嗡撚好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b3030c3684c0e38e43010911ced28b6ca285a","tid":1238982,"uid":1425,"like":284,"dislike":2,"score":282,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好呀, 冇左淋病老母香港人好難團結架"},{"pid":"3e096603996df5174b934d4226bbeb3a386c50ca","tid":1238982,"uid":48631,"like":55,"dislike":4,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"鳩up王又黎鳩up"},{"pid":"